tutorial:
Touch and hold the screen
to charge your rocket boots

When you think you've got
enough charge, let go to jump!

The more charge you have
the higher you jump!

It can take just the right
amount to save kitty!

Use the meter to measure
your jump charge!

Try to collect coins, you need
them to unlock later comics!

If you get stuck, you
can hit the reset button

You can use bouncies to help
you with hard to reach places!

Tap mid air to
open your parachute!

tilt the device to
steer the parachute!

Tap mid air to
use your grappling hook!

Titling your device
steers your swing!
